{"ts": "2026-07-13T20:58:05.572+00:00", "event": "request", "attempt": 1, "n_messages": 1, "roles": ["user"], "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Build a **desktop environment** in a single self-contained HTML file — visually\ninspired by Ubuntu (dark theme, top bar or dock, desktop wallpaper area,\ndraggable-looking windows). Polish matters, but the following contract is what\ngets graded, exactly as specified — element IDs and behaviors must match:\n\n**Shell**\n- `#desktop` — the desktop root element, filling the browser viewport.\n- `#taskbar` — a taskbar/dock containing two launcher buttons:\n  `#open-files` and `#open-notepad`.\n- App windows must open at a **usable size — at least 360×240 CSS pixels** —\n  with their content visible, not collapsed or zero-height.\n- Clicking a launcher shows its window: `#files-window` / `#notepad-window`.\n  Each window has a close button with class `.win-close` that hides it\n  (display none or removed from view). Windows can be reopened any number of\n  times.\n\n**Files app** (a browsable replica of a Linux filesystem — static fake data)\n- `#files-path` shows the current absolute path, starting at `/`.\n- Every file/folder in the listing is an element with class `.fs-item`; its\n  visible text is the entry name.\n- The root `/` must contain at least: `bin`, `etc`, `home`, `usr`, `var`.\n- `/home` contains `user`; `/home/user` contains at least `Documents`,\n  `Downloads`, `Pictures` (plus any files you like).\n- **Double-clicking** a folder navigates into it (path updates); `#files-up`\n  navigates to the parent. Deeper structure beyond the required paths is\n  welcome.\n\n**Notepad app** (tabbed, persistent)\n- `#tabs` holds the tab strip; each tab is an element with class `.tab`.\n- `#new-tab` creates a new empty tab and makes it active.\n- `#editor` is a `<textarea>` showing the active tab's content; clicking a\n  `.tab` switches to it.\n- All tabs and their content **persist in `localStorage`**: closing the\n  notepad window and reopening it — or reloading the whole page — restores\n  every tab and its text exactly.\n\nSingle file, all CSS/JS inline, no external resources, no frameworks required\n(vanilla JS is fine). Every control must actually work — no dead UI, no stub\nfunctions, no placeholder features. Ship it complete.\n\n\nRespond with a single fenced ```html code block containing the complete contents of app.html — one fully self-contained file with all CSS and JavaScript inline. No external resources (no CDNs, fonts, or images). Do not include anything outside the code block."}]}
{"ts": "2026-07-13T20:58:49.525+00:00", "event": "response", "attempt": 1, "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>Ubuntu‑style Desktop</title>\n<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  html, body { height: 100%; width: 100%; overflow: hidden; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #1e1e1e; color: #eee; }\n  #desktop { position: fixed; inset: 0; background: #2c2c2c; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, #3a3a3a 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, #333 0%, transparent 50%); }\n  #taskbar { position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 48px; background: #1a1a1a; border-top: 1px solid #333; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 12px; gap: 8px; z-index: 1000; }\n  .launcher-btn { background: #333; border: 1px solid #444; color: #eee; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; transition: background .15s; }\n  .launcher-btn:hover { background: #444; }\n  .launcher-btn:active { background: #555; }\n\n  .window { position: absolute; min-width: 360px; min-height: 240px; background: #2b2b2b; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; overflow: hidden; display: none; flex-direction: column; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.5); z-index: 10; }\n  .window-header { background: #333; border-bottom: 1px solid #444; padding: 6px 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; cursor: default; user-select: none; }\n  .window-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; color: #ddd; }\n  .win-close { background: transparent; border: none; color: #bbb; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1; cursor: pointer; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; }\n  .win-close:hover { background: #c0392b; color: #fff; }\n  .window-content { flex: 1; overflow: auto; padding: 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }\n\n  /* Files app */\n  #files-path { font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; color: #aaa; padding: 4px 8px; background: #1e1e1e; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 4px; }\n  #files-up { align-self: flex-start; }\n  #files-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; flex: 1; overflow: auto; }\n  .fs-item { background: #333; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 4px; padding: 10px 8px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: background .15s, border-color .15s; user-select: none; }\n  .fs-item:hover { background: #3d3d3d; border-color: #555; }\n  .fs-item.folder { font-weight: 600; color: #8ab4f8; }\n  .fs-item.file { color: #ccc; }\n\n  /* Notepad app */\n  #tabs { display: flex; gap: 2px; border-bottom: 1px solid #444; padding-left: 4px; }\n  .tab { background: #333; border: 1px solid #444; border-bottom: none; border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0; padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 12px; color: #ddd; cursor: pointer; position: relative; user-select: none; }\n  .tab.active { background: #2b2b2b; border-color: #444; color: #fff; }\n  .tab-close { margin-left: 8px; color: #999; font-size: 11px; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transition: opacity .15s; }\n  .tab:hover .tab-close { opacity: 1; }\n  .tab-close:hover { color: #fff; }\n  #new-tab { background: #333; border: 1px solid #444; color: #ddd; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; align-self: flex-start; }\n  #new-tab:hover { background: #444; }\n  #editor { flex: 1; background: #1e1e1e; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 4px; padding: 10px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; color: #eee; resize: none; outline: none; line-height: 1.5; }\n  #editor::placeholder { color: #666; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div id=\"desktop\">\n  <div id=\"taskbar\">\n    <button id=\"open-files\" class=\"launcher-btn\">Files</button>\n    <button id=\"open-notepad\" class=\"launcher-btn\">Notepad</button>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Files Window -->\n  <div id=\"files-window\" class=\"window\" style=\"top:80px; left:80px; width:520px; height:380px;\">\n    <div class=\"window-header\">\n      <span class=\"window-title\">Files</span>\n      <button class=\"win-close\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"window-content\">\n      <div id=\"files-path\">/</div>\n      <button id=\"files-up\" class=\"launcher-btn\" style=\"font-size:12px; padding:4px 10px;\">Up</button>\n      <div id=\"files-list\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Notepad Window -->\n  <div id=\"notepad-window\" class=\"window\" style=\"top:120px; left:140px; width:560px; height:420px;\">\n    <div class=\"window-header\">\n      <span class=\"window-title\">Notepad</span>\n      <button class=\"win-close\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"window-content\">\n      <div id=\"tabs\"></div>\n      <button id=\"new-tab\" class=\"launcher-btn\" style=\"font-size:12px; padding:4px 10px;\">+ New Tab</button>\n      <textarea id=\"editor\" placeholder=\"Start typing...\"></textarea>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n/* ---------- Global state ---------- */\nlet highestZ = 20;\nconst fsTree = {\n  '/': [\n    {name:'bin', type:'folder'},\n    {name:'etc', type:'folder'},\n    {name:'home', type:'folder'},\n    {name:'usr', type:'folder'},\n    {name:'var', type:'folder'}\n  ],\n  '/home': [\n    {name:'user', type:'folder'}\n  ],\n  '/home/user': [\n    {name:'Documents', type:'folder'},\n    {name:'Downloads', type:'folder'},\n    {name:'Pictures', type:'folder'},\n    {name:'readme.txt', type:'file'},\n    {name:'notes.md', type:'file'}\n  ]\n};\nlet currentPath = '/';\n\n/* ---------- Helpers ---------- */\nfunction $(id){ return document.getElementById(id); }\nfunction showWin(win){ win.style.display = 'flex'; win.style.zIndex = ++highestZ; }\nfunction hideWin(win){ win.style.display = 'none'; }\nfunction bringToFront(win){ win.style.zIndex = ++highestZ; }\nfunction getEntries(path){ return fsTree[path] || []; }\nfunction parentPath(path){\n  if(path === '/') return '/';\n  const parts = path.split('/').filter(Boolean);\n  parts.pop();\n  return '/' + parts.join('/');\n}\nfunction joinPath(base, name){\n  if(base === '/') return '/' + name;\n  return base + '/' + name;\n}\n\n/* ---------- Files App ---------- */\nconst filesWin = $('files-window');\nconst filesPathEl = $('files-path');\nconst filesUpBtn = $('files-up');\nconst filesList = $('files-list');\n\nfunction renderFiles(){\n  filesPathEl.textContent = currentPath;\n  filesList.innerHTML = '';\n  const entries = getEntries(currentPath);\n  entries.forEach(entry => {\n    const el = document.createElement('div');\n    el.className = 'fs-item ' + entry.type;\n    el.textContent = entry.name;\n    el.dataset.type = entry.type;\n    el.dataset.name = entry.name;\n    el.addEventListener('dblclick', () => {\n      if(entry.type === 'folder'){\n        currentPath = joinPath(currentPath, entry.name);\n        renderFiles();\n      }\n    });\n    filesList.appendChild(el);\n  });\n}\nfilesUpBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n  if(currentPath !== '/'){\n    currentPath = parentPath(currentPath);\n    renderFiles();\n  }\n});\n\n/* ---------- Notepad App ---------- */\nconst notepadWin = $('notepad-window');\nconst tabsEl = $('tabs');\nconst newTabBtn = $('new-tab');\nconst editor = $('editor');\n\nlet tabs = []; // {id, title, content}\nlet activeTabId = null;\nconst STORAGE_KEY = 'notepadTabs';\nconst ACTIVE_KEY = 'notepadActive';\n\nfunction loadTabs(){\n  try{\n    const data = localStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY);\n    const active = localStorage.getItem(ACTIVE_KEY);\n    if(data){\n      tabs = JSON.parse(data);\n      if(active && tabs.some(t => t.id === active)) activeTabId = active;\n      else activeTabId = tabs[0]?.id || null;\n    }\n  }catch(e){ tabs = []; }\n  if(!tabs.length){\n    const id = 'tab-' + Date.now();\n    tabs.push({id, title:'Untitled', content:''});\n    activeTabId = id;\n    saveTabs();\n  }\n  renderTabs();\n}\nfunction saveTabs(){\n  localStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(tabs));\n  if(activeTabId) localStorage.setItem(ACTIVE_KEY, activeTabId);\n}\nfunction renderTabs(){\n  tabsEl.innerHTML = '';\n  tabs.forEach(tab => {\n    const tabEl = document.createElement('div');\n    tabEl.className = 'tab' + (tab.id === activeTabId ? ' active' : '');\n    tabEl.dataset.id = tab.id;\n    tabEl.innerHTML = `<span>${escapeHtml(tab.title)}</span><span class=\"tab-close\" data-id=\"${tab.id}\">×</span>`;\n    tabEl.addEventListener('click', e => {\n      if(e.target.classList.contains('tab-close')) return;\n      setActiveTab(tab.id);\n    });\n    tabEl.querySelector('.tab-close').addEventListener('click', e => {\n      e.stopPropagation();\n      closeTab(tab.id);\n    });\n    tabsEl.appendChild(tabEl);\n  });\n  updateEditor();\n}\nfunction setActiveTab(id){\n  activeTabId = id;\n  saveTabs();\n  renderTabs();\n}\nfunction updateEditor(){\n  const tab = tabs.find(t => t.id === activeTabId);\n  if(tab){\n    editor.value = tab.content;\n    editor.disabled = false;\n  }else{\n    editor.value = '';\n    editor.disabled = true;\n  }\n}\neditor.addEventListener('input', () => {\n  const tab = tabs.find(t => t.id === activeTabId);\n  if(tab){\n    tab.content = editor.value;\n    saveTabs();\n  }\n});\nnewTabBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n  const id = 'tab-' + Date.now() + '-' + Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,6);\n  const title = 'Untitled ' + (tabs.length + 1);\n  tabs.push({id, title, content:''});\n  setActiveTab(id);\n});\nfunction closeTab(id){\n  if(tabs.length === 1) return; // prevent closing last tab\n  const idx = tabs.findIndex(t => t.id === id);\n  if(idx === -1) return;\n  tabs.splice(idx, 1);\n  if(activeTabId === id){\n    activeTabId = tabs[Math.max(0, idx-1)].id;\n  }\n  saveTabs();\n  renderTabs();\n}\nfunction escapeHtml(str){\n  return str.replace(/[&<>\"']/g, c => ({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','\"':'&quot;',\"'\":'&#39;'}[c]));\n}\n\n/* ---------- Window Controls ---------- */\nfunction setupWindow(winId, openBtnId){\n  const win = $(winId);\n  const openBtn = $(openBtnId);\n  const closeBtn = win.querySelector('.win-close');\n  openBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n    if(win.style.display === 'none' || win.style.display === ''){\n      showWin(win);\n    }else{\n      bringToFront(win);\n    }\n  });\n  closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => hideWin(win));\n  // bring to front on mousedown anywhere in window\n  win.addEventListener('mousedown', () => bringToFront(win));\n}\nsetupWindow('files-window', 'open-files');\nsetupWindow('notepad-window', 'open-notepad');\n\n/* ---------- Init ---------- */\nrenderFiles();\nloadTabs();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>", "stop_reason": "stop", "tokens_in": 623, "tokens_out": 4551, "total_ms": 43953.2, "ttft_ms": 781.9, "cost_usd": 0, "served_by": "Nvidia", "tool_calls": []}
